And that mission fell completely flat.

53
00:03:19,663 --> 00:03:23,464
So this is a somewhat personal talk, because ever since Leia, I've been looking for help

54
00:03:23,504 --> 00:03:24,044
in this area.

55
00:03:24,624 --> 00:03:29,126
