56
00:03:29,266 --> 00:03:30,626
on what the actual problem is.

57
00:03:32,084 --> 00:03:35,605
So what I've come to realize or think is that it's not a singular problem,

58
00:03:35,625 --> 00:03:38,486
there's actually two distinctly different approaches to character creation.

59
00:03:38,986 --> 00:03:41,226
And both have their own philosophical baggage attached,

60
00:03:41,266 --> 00:03:42,667
they all have their own ideologies,

61
00:03:43,207 --> 00:03:45,588
which makes it kind of difficult to talk about the subject, right?

62
00:03:45,608 --> 00:03:46,568
Because it's kind of divisive.

63
00:03:46,708 --> 00:03:49,909
